<TEXT>
<P>
A 28-year-old man was shot to death as he waited for friends outside a North 
Hollywood convenience store, Los Angeles police reported Sunday. 
</P>
<P>
Octaviano Robles Hernandez was shot about 11:45 p.m. Saturday as he sat in the 
