<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Phil and Steve Mahre made history of sorts when they raced against each other 
in the finals of a slalom at Waterville Valley, N.H. It was the first time the 
twins have met in the finals of a pro skiing tour event. Phil won, overcoming 
Steve's .57 second advantage from the first run to finish .151 ahead in the 
second run. 
</P>
