-- FOREIGN POLICY -- CHINA; BUSH, GEORGE; HUMAN RIGHTS -- CHINA; SCOWCROFT, 
BRENT; EAGLEBURGER, LAWRENCE S; FOREIGN STUDENTS; CHINESE -- UNITED STATES; 
UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- USSR 
</P>
