Employees May Buy Slice of Domino's: Domino's Pizza Inc. owner Tom Monaghan 
said Domino's has retained Goldman Sachs &amp; Co. and J. P. Morgan &amp; Co. 
to study the feasibility of an employee stock ownership plan. He said he will 
decide whether to implement an ESOP on completion of the study and will remain 
