a personal, almost folksy tone: "Make check payable to Robert L. 'Bob' Citron." 
. . . Citron has been sending out bills like this since he was first elected 18 
years ago. Not to promote himself, he said, but because he accepts tax payments 
for 175 different agencies. . . . Still, Irvine-based political consultant 
